## Installation

### Download from the App Store (iPhone and iPad)

1. Open the App Store on your iPhone or iPad.
2. Search for "Image to PDF - PDF Converter+" in the search bar.
3. Tap on the app icon in the search results.
4. On the app page, tap the "Get" or "Download" button.
5. Authenticate with your Apple ID, if prompted.
6. Wait for the app to download and install on your device.
7. Once installed, the app icon will appear on your home screen.

## Features

Image to PDF - PDF Converter+ offers a feature to convert Image from your gallery to PDF in a second. Explore the following capabilities:

### Image to PDF

All you need to Pick the Image(unlimited) from the Gallery using the browse button that you want to convert into PDF, Customize PDF settings and convert it. It is fast and accurate. By default, it will store in your PDF Library to access. 

### PDF Library

Once Image converted into PDF, it will store in the second screen - PDF Library. You can store, view, delete, add new PDF file and share. 

### PDF settings

Using PDF settings, you can customize the PDF Position and Margin of the PDF to convert from Image to PDF.

